00:18:22,760 --> 00:18:26,700
 I volunteer to join Light Chaser Rescue Team,

220
00:18:26,700 --> 00:18:29,428
 in a volunteering spirit of

221
00:18:29,428 --> 00:18:33,160
 devotion, friendship, progress, and mutual help.

222
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:36,628
 I'll train hard and industriously.

223
00:18:36,628 --> 00:18:38,771
 In times of various crises,

224
00:18:38,771 --> 00:18:42,728
 I'll do my best to save lives.

225
00:18:47,142 --> 00:18:55,942
♫  I hope the wind can blow through the lane  ♫

226
00:18:55,942 --> 00:19:02,057
♫  And rest in your arms  ♫

227
00:19:02,057 --> 00:19:11,085
♫  The one who loves you and you love 
 will always be with you  ♫

228
00:19:11,085 --> 00:19:18,620
♫  It's a stable place for you when turning back  ♫

229
00:19:18,620 --> 00:19:22,214
♫  Catching the floating stars  ♫

230
00:19:22,214 --> 00:19:26,210
♫  Watching as the memories flash by  ♫

231
00:19:26,210 --> 00:19:29,650
♫  Traveling through market scenes  ♫

232
