Uncle Luodan, your blood sugar and blood pressure are a bit high.

234
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:13,128
You have to keep taking this medicine.

235
00:20:13,128 --> 00:20:15,228
I'll give you some medicine first.

236
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:18,350
Drugs are toxic.

237
00:20:18,350 --> 00:20:21,057
I can't take them every day.

238
00:20:23,100 --> 00:20:26,671
Long-term high blood pressure will impair

239
00:20:26,671 --> 00:20:29,310
the heart and the kidneys.

240
00:20:29,310 --> 00:20:32,771
So, you must take this medicine.

241
00:20:46,420 --> 00:20:48,120
Do you like it?

242
00:20:59,259 --> 00:21:00,720
Take it.

243
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:06,120
Little Tashi, you must study hard in the future and attend school.

244
00:21:06,120 --> 00:21:08,199
Thank you, Doctor.

245
00:21:09,060 --> 00:21:10,240
Come on, you kid.

246
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:11,820
It's okay.

247
00:21:11,820 --> 00:21:15,039
They're all small gifts for the kids.

248
00:21:15,039 --> 00:21:17,400
Make sure you keep taking your medication.

249
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:21,271
Thank you, Dr. Zhan.

250
00:21:23,820 --> 00:21:25,514
Let's go.

251
00:21:31,900 --> 00:21:33,590
What's this, An?

252
00:21:33,590 --> 00:21:35,385
The masks I had my family send to me.

253
00:21:35,385 --> 00:21:37,700
I can't buy them here.

254
00:21:42,450 --> 00:21:46,971
This place is not like Linjiang.

255
00:21:46,971 --> 00:21:49,571
You signed up to support this place with me.

256
00:21:49,571 --> 00:21:52,214
- You're regretting it? 
 - How would I?

257
00:21:52,214 --> 00:21:53,928
I'm here to study and train with you.

258
00:21:53,928 --> 00:21:56,357
People in our department all envy me.

259
00:21:56,357 --> 00:21:59,970
Xu Zirui said he'd sign up for the next session.

260
00:21:59,970 --> 00:22:01,585
He just got married.

261
00:22:01,585 --> 00:22:03,071
Is he willing to support this place?

