00:22:03,071 --> 00:22:04,657
Lu supports him.

263
00:22:04,657 --> 00:22:07,585
The students you've trained are all good.

264
00:22:07,585 --> 00:22:12,110
By the way, I thought you said a new colleague would come to help us.

265
00:22:12,110 --> 00:22:14,771
He should be here in a couple of days.

266
00:22:23,300 --> 00:22:25,371

267
00:22:26,690 --> 00:22:28,371
Bye.

268
00:22:47,380 --> 00:22:51,342
- Let me see. 
 - It hurts.

269
00:22:52,857 --> 00:22:54,814
Hold on.

270
00:22:56,539 --> 00:22:58,159
It hurts.

271
00:23:01,970 --> 00:23:04,442
- It's okay. 
 - What are you doing?

272
00:23:04,442 --> 00:23:06,171
He dislocated his arm. I'm fixing it.

273
00:23:06,228 --> 00:23:08,240
I saw my son crying.

274
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:12,520
I won't let you go until you make it clear.

275
00:23:12,520 --> 00:23:14,720
I was just fixing him.

276
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:16,770
But I saw...

277
00:23:16,770 --> 00:23:18,371
I just saw my son crying.

278
00:23:18,371 --> 00:23:20,328
- Which hand is hurt? 
 - This one.

279
00:23:20,328 --> 00:23:22,585
Ask him if you don't believe me. I'm the doctor here.

280
00:23:22,585 --> 00:23:24,080
- Can you move it? 
 - Look at my clothes.

281
00:23:24,090 --> 00:23:25,428
I'm not here to hurt Zhuo.

282
00:23:25,428 --> 00:23:27,420
- Does it hurt? 
 - No.

283
00:23:27,420 --> 00:23:30,340
Dad, it's not hurting.

284
00:23:30,340 --> 00:23:31,960
It doesn't hurt?

285
00:23:31,960 --> 00:23:33,160
That's right.

286
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:34,742
This doctor wasn't lying to you.

287
00:23:34,742 --> 00:23:37,250
She did relocate your son's joint.

288
00:23:37,250 --> 00:23:38,620
Is that so?

289
00:23:38,620 --> 00:23:40,720
Cai Yuxiao.

290
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:42,471
It's been a while.

291
00:23:43,630 --> 00:23:45,157
I'm really sorry.

292
00:23:45,157 --> 00:23:47,000
There was just a slight misunderstanding.

293
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:48,840
I'm sorry.

294
00:23:51,860 --> 00:23:53,028
This is my phone number.

295
00:23:53,042 --> 00:23:55,871
Feel free to call me if your son is uncomfortable.

296
00:23:55,871 --> 00:23:58,720
Thank you. Thank you.

297
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:01,257
Let's go, kid. Get up.

298
00:24:03,530 --> 00:24:05,500
Thank you so much!

299
00:24:06,720 --> 00:24:09,700
Dr. Zhan, I'm here to report for duty.

300
00:24:09,700 --> 00:24:11,210
Don't you want me here?

301
00:24:11,210 --> 00:24:12,730
How's that possible?

302
00:24:12,730 --> 00:24:15,820
I just didn't expect the new colleague to be you.

303
00:24:15,820 --> 00:24:17,350
I'll take you to the dormitory.

304
00:24:17,350 --> 00:24:18,771
Okay.

305
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:30,580
You must be tired from the trip.

306
00:24:30,580 --> 00:24:32,630
I've got some hot water for you.

307
00:24:32,630 --> 00:24:34,085
Thank you.

308
00:24:35,019 --> 00:24:36,980
You've changed a lot.

309
00:24:36,980 --> 00:24:39,660
I hardly recognized you.

310
00:24:39,660 --> 00:24:41,739
Really?

311
00:24:41,739 --> 00:24:44,240
Sometimes I look at myself in the mirror,

312
00:24:44,240 --> 00:24:46,740
I find that I've changed a lot.

313
00:24:47,720 --> 00:24:48,942
Here, drink some water.

314
00:24:48,942 --> 00:24:50,585
Okay.

315
00:24:50,585 --> 00:24:52,530
Thank you.

316
00:24:53,550 --> 00:24:55,371
You're hurt?

317
00:24:58,160 --> 00:25:03,328
I got a minor injury when I worked as a Doctor Without Borders in the war zone.

318
00:25:05,110 --> 00:25:06,900
You were so badly wounded.

319
00:25:06,900 --> 00:25:09,457
What kind of mission was it?

320
00:25:11,720 --> 00:25:13,350
The place was in a war.

321
00:25:13,350 --> 00:25:17,085
Suddenly a shell exploded right next to us.

322
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:22,114
I didn't expect you to go to such a dangerous place.

323
00:25:24,070 --> 00:25:25,771
Let's talk about you.

324
00:25:25,771 --> 00:25:28,214
Why did you come here?

325
00:25:28,879 --> 00:25:30,985
You know,

326
00:25:30,985 --> 00:25:34,100
I've always wanted to support remote areas.

327
00:25:35,357 --> 00:25:38,230
But the conditions here are not like that of Linjiang.

328
00:25:38,230 --> 00:25:40,600
Just let me know if you need anything.

329
00:25:40,600 --> 00:25:43,450
I'll get it to you if I have it.

330
00:25:43,450 --> 00:25:44,799
No need.

331
00:25:44,799 --> 00:25:46,739
It's already good.

332
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:49,342
Okay, go clean up.

333
00:25:49,342 --> 00:25:51,340
Get some rest.

334
00:25:51,340 --> 00:25:54,620
I'll talk to you about what you need to do tomorrow.

335
00:25:54,620 --> 00:25:56,100
Okay.

336
00:26:23,559 --> 00:26:27,019
 Dad, why did you answer my call so quickly?

337
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:31,600
I thought it was time for you to call.

338
00:26:31,600 --> 00:26:35,760
Good for you. What if I work late next time?

339
00:26:35,760 --> 00:26:38,185
 I've left the team's business to Luo Ben.

340
00:26:38,185 --> 00:26:40,585
 I'm not busy now. I have time to wait for you.

341
00:26:40,585 --> 00:26:42,771
I just think about you.

342
00:26:42,771 --> 00:26:44,628
You're out there by yourself.

343
00:26:44,628 --> 00:26:46,328
 Take care of yourself.

344
00:26:46,328 --> 00:26:49,210
Don't worry, I'm fine here.

345
00:26:49,210 --> 00:26:52,070
I work at sunrise and rest at sunset.

346
00:26:52,070 --> 00:26:54,785
I keep a regular schedule. And I have a healthy diet.

347
00:26:54,785 --> 00:26:57,257
I'm really here to preserve my health.

348
00:26:57,257 --> 00:27:00,730
 But I worry if you took your medicine.

349
00:27:00,730 --> 00:27:02,670
 Including the habit of drinking tea at night.

350
00:27:02,670 --> 00:27:04,590
 Did you get rid of it?

351
00:27:04,590 --> 00:27:06,600
 You can't drink tea at night anymore.

352
00:27:06,600 --> 00:27:10,342
 It'll burden the heart and kidneys.

353
00:27:10,342 --> 00:27:13,414
 And it's very bad for your stomach.

354
00:27:13,414 --> 00:27:17,371
 Do you hear that? And you can't drink alcohol.

355
00:27:17,371 --> 00:27:20,620
I quit drinking. The tea is for the day.

356
00:27:20,620 --> 00:27:23,660
Don't worry. I quit drinking.

357
00:27:23,660 --> 00:27:25,728
That's good.

358
00:27:25,728 --> 00:27:29,499
Guess who I met today.

359
00:27:29,499 --> 00:27:31,679
Is it someone I know?

360
00:27:32,340 --> 00:27:34,014
Cai Yuxiao.

361
00:27:35,480 --> 00:27:36,720
Cai?

362
00:27:36,720 --> 00:27:39,028
 So he went to support there?

363
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:41,760
Yeah.

364
00:27:41,760 --> 00:27:43,939
I didn't expect to see him here.

365
00:27:43,939 --> 00:27:45,780
But he's changed a lot.

366
00:27:45,780 --> 00:27:47,259
I hardly recognized him.

367
00:27:47,259 --> 00:27:49,599
Give my best regards to him.

368
00:27:49,599 --> 00:27:53,659
 Yan, Luo Ben asked about you today.

369
00:27:53,659 --> 00:27:56,180
 I know cellphone reception there is bad.

370
00:27:56,180 --> 00:27:59,400
Maybe you should take some time to talk to him.

371
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:01,800
 He's very concerned about you.

372
00:28:02,520 --> 00:28:05,279
Dad, Cai Yuxiao just arrived here.

373
00:28:05,279 --> 00:28:07,542
I'll show him around later.

374
00:28:07,542 --> 00:28:09,890
I've got to go.

375
00:29:13,340 --> 00:29:18,060
The Light Chaser Rescue Team has been growing so fast lately.

376
00:29:18,060 --> 00:29:21,210
We've participated in one rescue operation after another.

377
00:29:21,210 --> 00:29:26,885
We successfully completed the tasks that leaders and the public gave to us.

378
00:29:26,885 --> 00:29:29,000
I've counted it.

379
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:34,590
As of today, the Light Chaser Rescue Teams in the whole country this year

380
00:29:34,590 --> 00:29:39,357
have been a part of more than 6,000 rescues.

381
00:29:41,899 --> 00:29:45,659
This is Mr. Robert, an international rescue expert.

382
00:29:45,659 --> 00:29:50,657
From today, Mr. Robert will guide us in training.

383
00:29:50,657 --> 00:29:54,699
From getting visas, exit formalities, to standardizing technical movements

384
00:29:54,699 --> 00:29:57,257
and rescue process, etc.

385
00:29:57,257 --> 00:29:59,580
In short, everything is fine and detailed,

386
00:29:59,580 --> 00:30:04,414
and everything is carried out in accordance with international rescue standards.

387
00:31:01,359 --> 00:31:02,779
You are just leaving?

388
00:31:02,779 --> 00:31:04,180
Why not think it over?

389
00:31:04,180 --> 00:31:06,499
I'd like you to stay.

390
00:31:07,140 --> 00:31:09,879
Thank you so much. I've made up my mind.

391
00:31:11,790 --> 00:31:13,185
Is Luo Ben so important?

392
00:31:13,185 --> 00:31:17,400
Even if you can't be together, you can still be good colleagues.

393
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:18,400
That's not necessary.

394
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:20,580
It was my plan to study in England.

395
00:31:20,580 --> 00:31:22,939
Now it's time.

396
00:31:22,939 --> 00:31:24,250
Old Gao,

397
00:31:24,250 --> 00:31:27,720
maybe Ariel will meet a man better than Luo Ben in the UK.

398
00:31:27,720 --> 00:31:29,740
Don't worry about her.

399
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:33,290
I'm leaving, then.

400
00:31:33,290 --> 00:31:34,757
Take care.

401
00:31:59,620 --> 00:32:01,339
 Have a safe trip.

402
00:32:15,360 --> 00:32:17,650
Take one. And you.

403
00:32:17,650 --> 00:32:19,114
Come on. Come on. Here.

404
00:32:19,114 --> 00:32:20,985
Who wants it?

405
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:25,842
Count how many I have in my hand.

406
00:32:25,842 --> 00:32:27,657
How many are there?

407
00:32:29,150 --> 00:32:30,171
Thank you.

408
00:32:30,171 --> 00:32:31,960
Uncle.

409
00:32:31,960 --> 00:32:34,019
Pass these out.

410
00:32:35,340 --> 00:32:37,200
 Here.

411
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:39,228
Why are you here?

412
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:44,128
I didn't expect you to be the kids' friend so soon.

413
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:46,728
This is my experience.

414
00:32:46,728 --> 00:32:48,457
Whenever I go somewhere new,

415
00:32:48,457 --> 00:32:51,000
I'll keep a good relationship with the local kids.

416
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:53,714
So I can start the work easily.

417
00:32:59,930 --> 00:33:04,328
I feel you're different but also the same.

418
00:33:04,328 --> 00:33:08,985
You're still Cai Yuxiao who thinks everything through.

419
00:33:10,550 --> 00:33:13,030
I think you've changed a lot.

420
00:33:13,030 --> 00:33:14,870
Have I?

421
00:33:14,870 --> 00:33:18,442
Now you think about others.

422
00:33:22,620 --> 00:33:26,240
I was too cold and selfish before.

423
00:33:26,240 --> 00:33:28,420
I never thought of others.

424
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:36,000
No, it was my fault.

425
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:37,980
I was selfish.

426
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:40,971
I did a lot of wrong things to you.

427
00:33:40,971 --> 00:33:42,490
I should apologize to you.

428
00:33:42,490 --> 00:33:44,385
It's over.

429
00:33:45,590 --> 00:33:47,328
What about your parents?

430
00:33:49,770 --> 00:33:52,070
After we left Linjiang,

431
00:33:52,070 --> 00:33:55,000
I took them back to their hometown.

432
00:33:55,000 --> 00:33:59,060
Not long after that, my mother passed away.

433
00:34:01,060 --> 00:34:03,742
I took care of my family's stuff

434
00:34:03,742 --> 00:34:06,214
and arranged for my father to settle down,

435
00:34:06,214 --> 00:34:08,128
then I went out.

436
00:34:09,380 --> 00:34:12,885
Why did you join Doctors Without Borders?

437
00:34:14,330 --> 00:34:16,114
After I left my hometown,

438
00:34:16,114 --> 00:34:20,319
I traveled around aimlessly.

439
00:34:20,319 --> 00:34:23,585
I went to some places with poor medical conditions

440
00:34:23,585 --> 00:34:26,980
where I participated in the international volunteer medical service.

441
00:34:26,980 --> 00:34:32,760
I worked and helped the locals in need with them.

442
00:34:33,459 --> 00:34:35,079
Later,

443
00:34:36,371 --> 00:34:40,971
I found I lived a full life there.

444
00:34:40,971 --> 00:34:44,850
I felt I was quite worthy.

445
00:34:44,850 --> 00:34:48,742
So, I applied to join this organization.

446
00:34:49,580 --> 00:34:51,385
What about you?

447
00:34:51,385 --> 00:34:53,528
Why did you come here?

448
00:34:58,660 --> 00:35:00,400
I broke up with him.

449
00:35:20,120 --> 00:35:22,600
Our company has gotten through the difficulties.

450
00:35:22,600 --> 00:35:25,828
The new project is starting up again.

451
00:35:26,990 --> 00:35:29,714
You're busy in the company all day.

452
00:35:29,714 --> 00:35:34,200
Your dad won't be back home until the end of the year.

453
00:35:34,200 --> 00:35:37,328
It's hard to have a meal with you two.

454
00:35:37,328 --> 00:35:42,057
Mom, since you've said that, I'll send your instructions to my dad.

455
00:35:42,057 --> 00:35:43,371
I'll ask him to come back soon.

456
00:35:43,371 --> 00:35:45,271
I won't have a meeting tomorrow.

457
00:35:45,271 --> 00:35:46,571
I'll spend some time with you.

458
00:35:46,620 --> 00:35:48,057
Do you want to go shopping?

459
00:35:48,057 --> 00:35:51,020
Or play cards?

460
00:35:51,020 --> 00:35:52,799
Not tomorrow.

461
00:35:52,799 --> 00:35:55,180
Maybe another time.

462
00:35:55,180 --> 00:35:56,580
Come on.

463
00:35:56,580 --> 00:35:58,857
Now you don't care what's going on outside.

464
00:35:58,857 --> 00:36:01,200
You left the company to me.

465
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:03,114
You've been preserving your health at home.

466
00:36:03,114 --> 00:36:06,142
What's so important that you can't put it off?

467
00:36:08,160 --> 00:36:10,585
I've got a date with Ding Dingding.

468
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:15,880
- Dingding? 
 - Yeah, Dingding.

469
00:36:15,880 --> 00:36:17,910
Your girlfriend.

470
00:36:17,910 --> 00:36:21,928
She's going to the school to sign books for the kids tomorrow.

471
00:36:21,928 --> 00:36:23,760
She asked me to go with her.

472
00:36:23,760 --> 00:36:25,659
I agreed.

473
00:36:29,530 --> 00:36:31,210
My girlfriend?

474
00:36:31,210 --> 00:36:33,657
Mom, do you mean Dingding?

475
00:36:34,839 --> 00:36:37,659
Do you have other girlfriends?

476
00:36:41,370 --> 00:36:42,585
Mom, eat... eat more.

477
00:36:42,585 --> 00:36:43,785
Here, eat more.

478
00:36:43,785 --> 00:36:45,050
You eat. Don't care...

479
00:36:45,050 --> 00:36:46,240
All right. Enough.

480
00:36:46,240 --> 00:36:47,700
Mom, uh, I'm full.

481
00:36:47,700 --> 00:36:49,400
I'm going out.

482
00:36:49,400 --> 00:36:52,142
You haven't eaten any.

483
00:37:08,459 --> 00:37:10,019
 Dingding!

484
00:37:12,699 --> 00:37:16,400
 - Dingding!  
 - I'm coming.

485
00:37:18,128 --> 00:37:19,828
My mom is allowing me to be with you, Dingding.

486
00:37:19,828 --> 00:37:22,600
You're strangling me!

487
00:37:22,600 --> 00:37:25,314
Dingding, my mom admits that you're my girlfriend.

488
00:37:25,314 --> 00:37:26,342
Really?

489
00:37:26,342 --> 00:37:28,971
I'm so happy, Dingding.

490
00:37:31,140 --> 00:37:32,360
Put me down.

491
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:36,239
What's up? What's so exciting?

492
00:37:36,239 --> 00:37:37,942
My mom allowed me to be with Dingding.

493
00:37:37,942 --> 00:37:39,828
We can get the license properly.

494
00:37:39,828 --> 00:37:42,942
Luo Ben, come to our wedding by then.

495
00:37:43,839 --> 00:37:45,480
Congratulations!

496
00:37:48,390 --> 00:37:49,785
Why does he look unhappy?

497
00:37:49,785 --> 00:37:51,785
Come on. He broke up.

498
00:37:51,785 --> 00:37:53,560
But you send a wedding invitation to him.

499
00:37:53,560 --> 00:37:56,720
I'm sorry. I was so excited that I forgot about it.

500
00:37:56,720 --> 00:37:59,071
But don't worry about it. The captain put it all out there.

501
00:37:59,071 --> 00:38:01,540
Once it works itself out, the right people will be together sooner or later.

502
00:38:01,540 --> 00:38:03,040
Just like us.

503
00:38:03,040 --> 00:38:04,980
It's not easy for him and Yan.

504
00:38:04,980 --> 00:38:07,242
Yan went to such a faraway place not long after they were together.

505
00:38:07,242 --> 00:38:08,779
It's hard to see her.

506
00:38:08,779 --> 00:38:12,440
If it were you, I would go to you wherever you are.

507
00:38:12,440 --> 00:38:13,479
Really?

508
00:38:13,479 --> 00:38:15,260
Of course, it's true.

509
00:38:47,870 --> 00:38:50,990

510
00:39:16,200 --> 00:39:17,519
It's nice.

511
00:39:17,519 --> 00:39:20,260
I'll do it with you later.

512
00:39:22,240 --> 00:39:24,060
Your leg has recovered well.

513
00:39:24,060 --> 00:39:28,059
I think your training performance is almost as good as before.

514
00:39:28,059 --> 00:39:31,939
I was doing training when you were at work.

515
00:39:31,939 --> 00:39:33,780
Good for you.

516
00:39:36,799 --> 00:39:39,099
Did Guoguo make this bracelet for you?

517
00:39:40,379 --> 00:39:41,819
Yeah.

518
00:39:41,819 --> 00:39:43,060
She doesn't let me take it off.

519
00:39:43,060 --> 00:39:45,428
I told her that I was going to work and performing tasks.

520
00:39:45,428 --> 00:39:48,157
It's easy to lose it. I asked her if I could wear it at home.

521
00:39:48,157 --> 00:39:50,285
She said no. She was angry with me.

522
00:39:50,285 --> 00:39:52,514
She asked me to take a picture to send to her every two hours.

523
00:39:52,514 --> 00:39:54,214
To prove that I'm always wearing it.

524
00:39:54,214 --> 00:39:56,171
Look, kids now are...

525
00:39:56,171 --> 00:39:58,180
She's so cute.

526
00:39:58,180 --> 00:40:03,842
You don't know I've never envied you anything before I met Guoguo.

527
00:40:03,842 --> 00:40:07,228
Until she became a flower girl in Luo Yuan's wedding.

528
00:40:07,228 --> 00:40:10,039
I instantly became her fan.

529
00:40:10,039 --> 00:40:13,319
If I had such a lovely daughter like you,

530
00:40:13,319 --> 00:40:15,600
I'd be at home with her every weekend.

531
00:40:15,600 --> 00:40:17,028
I wouldn't come to train.

532
00:40:17,028 --> 00:40:19,885
If you like a daughter, you and Zhan Yan should have a baby now.

533
00:40:19,885 --> 00:40:22,885
No one else is as close as your kid.

534
